Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:30.04,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.12,0:00:36.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:44.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:51.33,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:01:00.07,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:05.58,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:10.52,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:15.86,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.29,0:01:22.89,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.07,0:01:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂流至某座无人岛的强他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.84,0:01:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一边克服着 饥饿 干旱 腹泻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:32.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,初吻 第二次的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及娜蒂亚的任性等重重难关
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:39.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,过着自力更生的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:42.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却由于突然登陆的台风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.59,0:01:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毁掉了他们建构起来的文明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.06,0:01:49.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然而塞翁失马 焉知非福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:52.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一座巨大的岛屿出现在 穷途末路的他们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:02:00.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们与重逢的三人组以及艾尔顿 在新的岛屿上过着和平的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 只要有两人以上同时在一起 想不发生问题都很难
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这份和平能维持到什么时候呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:13.41,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,29 大王对大王
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行 求求您别走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是梦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:31.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 吵醒你了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:33.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你作恶梦了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.34,0:02:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,梦到再也无法相见的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:45.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想我可能是世界上 最不幸的女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.72,0:02:49.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也很有那个资格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你还有个人陪在身边 所以还算好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有强这个体贴的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早上醒来就一定能见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或许你会认为很理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.54,0:03:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那其实是最高级的享受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然你看看我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:13.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱上一位自己高攀不上的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:16.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在爱情开花结果前便已阴阳两隔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我并不想 随时都和他在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是因为现在情况特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你迟早会面临 希望他随时都在身旁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.19,0:03:30.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但那时他不见得 还是会在你伸手可及的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在不也有许多男人 就在你伸手可及的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:40.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经看中它很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.14,0:03:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我本来就想留到最后再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已经吃下一堆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然了 这些鱼是我钓的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.51,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是钓竿是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:54.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,连用来烤鱼的炉子 也是我做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？\N你有意见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.69,0:04:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然就在身边 但我总还有选择的权利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是命运吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.03,0:04:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这世上有两种人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,运气好的人与不好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要来杯饭后的红茶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你说我算哪一种？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微冒犯一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你会看手相吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 我完全不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:37.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.86,0:04:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,运的好坏常会因为当时情况 而出现重大改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,特别是围绕在身边的男性 会带来最大的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,运这种东西 是可以凭自己的力量改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大人好讨厌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.08,0:05:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么运气的 鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不觉得他们老是 对一些无聊的东西很在意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每个人都是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.19,0:05:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是要活下去 就得这样做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.93,0:05:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人是没办法独自生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家要生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就必须克服困难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以及做出许多忍让才行\N强
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都是拿那支牙刷刷牙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:33.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那支牙刷是我平常在用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.99,0:05:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这位仁兄 麻烦你让让
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要跑来我的地盘啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:56.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么时候规定的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.61,0:05:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还用说吗 从很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:02.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是几年几月几日 几点几分几秒规定的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:04.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,9999兆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,9999亿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,9999万
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.49,0:06:12.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,9999年前就规定好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.19,0:06:16.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是谁规定的？ 地球可没那么久的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我规定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地球明明还没出现 你就活着啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,少啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 不准你进到这边
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这条就是边界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那空中又怎么算？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空中也不可以跨过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,话说回来 那两个人到底是怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们在吵架吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.62,0:06:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就是小孩子在吵嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好幼稚喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝 拜托你想点办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我为什么老是这么没男人运呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,尼莫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好吗 葛兰迪丝小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心爱的尼莫先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:25.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知现在身处何方？ 正在做些什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王真是的 兴奋成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是发现什么好东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.57,0:08:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.47,0:08:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也过来这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:08.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晒晒太阳比较舒服喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.81,0:08:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用了 我不想再晒得更黑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 是葛兰迪丝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好低级喔 竟然偷窥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她将瓶中信放流到海上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:31.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她用情真的那么深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:35.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的那么不懂女人心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我是男生啊 怎么可能会懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你根本就不试着去懂 每次都这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:45.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:47.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以偷吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我这才不是偷吃 是试吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.78,0:08:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那么…味道如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,棒极了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.82,0:08:59.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可以媲美真正的厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能得到您的称赞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在下感到荣幸之至 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的是个有钱又有地位的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:10.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为有钱又有地位的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,厨艺应该不会这么棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.51,0:09:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是因为我明白 真正的人间美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在英国的时候 曾经尝尽了豪华的美食世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.02,0:09:26.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些美味已经渗入我的舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我能做出这些精湛的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.12,0:09:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等将来你长大成为一位美女后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.73,0:09:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我艾尔顿伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会招待你享用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.36,0:09:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃到足以溶化身心的 英国皇家风味晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.41,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 你抓到螃蟹了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.92,0:10:01.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可真幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子沙拉就能升级成 蟹肉沙拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:09.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.59,0:10:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是在下使出浑身解数 烹调出来的英国风味午餐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,请各位尽情享用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不吃吗？很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是\N说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.78,0:10:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不准学我！\N不准学我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森！\N韩森！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天我实在忍不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然这样 那就不用再忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.00,0:10:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,决斗吧！\N决斗吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用不着那么杀气腾腾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该要和平一点 暴力是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.70,0:10:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,例如来场竞赛如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竞赛？\N竞赛？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.54,0:10:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回溯人类的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.54,0:10:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自古希腊时代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两国之间若有纠纷 就会互推代表以竞赛解决
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:05.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,伟大的人类庆典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.78,0:11:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奥林匹克运动会 也是因此而诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,英国也有马术这项贵族竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.59,0:11:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么说来 这里也有 能够用来竞赛的动物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是大王只有一只啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.00,0:11:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能够战胜大王的就只有大王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.07,0:11:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森只要靠自己的力量 做出一只大王就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:30.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么我得干那种事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是所谓的平衡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,平衡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:41.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,桑森就靠体力来锻炼大王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.35,0:11:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,韩森则是靠科学知识 制作出机械金属大王
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.56,0:11:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再由这两者来一较高下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有道理\N有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都几岁的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还在孩子们面前争吵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,实在不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:58.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里就用你们的力量与技术 来一较高下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不也比较和平吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在喝什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山羊奶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.39,0:12:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,羊奶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.13,0:12:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这只山羊是哪里来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在森林里发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.54,0:12:34.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要对其他人保密喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被其他人发现 它会被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前每次不都是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:48.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也没有每次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再说 好不容易有羊奶喝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把这只山羊杀掉 未免太可惜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们真的不会吃掉它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧 他已经闻风而来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.90,0:13:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不是山羊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以 这只山羊不是食物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.24,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你抓到的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不是抓来的呢 我们是成为了朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:17.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.05,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你要是敢把它烤来吃 我绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厉害喔 你真的能和动物沟通耶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:31.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是后来才听得懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.86,0:13:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,动物们的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在我还4 5岁的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我坐在正前往巡回各地的 马戏团马车上看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我感情很好的斯莫基 被人带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为斯莫基已经老了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们把对马戏团 没用处的斯莫基…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.59,0:14:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,它说它不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我救救它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是我却什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才渐渐能明白动物们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.48,0:14:23.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你才会没办法吃肉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们或许认为 吃肉是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我都会想到 它们是惨遭杀害的动物们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 你好可怜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们根本听不懂 动物们在说什么不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.59,0:14:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么啦 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没听到我的声音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王 快跑 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站起来 大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大爷我一定会唤醒你 沉眠在血液中的野性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.88,0:14:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先来个20趟100公尺冲刺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.84,0:14:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.65,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？大王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不跑的话我就会输耶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快给我醒来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.56,0:15:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,站起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:09.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后给我战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算我求你 只要站起来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.84,0:15:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你照我的话去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王弟弟 我只要你醒来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.19,0:15:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一个晚上就完成到这种程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我果然是个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.29,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种速度一定就连 真正的大王也比不上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来就是外观要怎么处理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:53.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,颜色就用意大利红吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:03.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,发生什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.95,0:16:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的心中有只 令人万念俱灰的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为那只虫子害得我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,并不是虫子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而是你正在挂念着某个人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.27,0:16:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,至今我明明不断追寻着爱情 为了爱情而活
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.71,0:16:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让我活下去的精神粮食 如今却消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱情是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱情是要靠自己主动寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若只会痴痴地等待 是不会有机会的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:43.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你自己不也曾那么说过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命运是要凭自己的力量去改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.87,0:16:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:04.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我这辈子唯一一次的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,问题是那种机械做的假大王 并不是简单就做得出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这点不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是我从韩森那里摸来的 机械设计图
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你也真是卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这存在着构造性的缺点耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根据这张图来看 必须靠外部供给电源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:35.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有办法改良吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要制作出小型电池 放在机械内部就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你做得出来吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.38,0:17:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 我们赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.02,0:17:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你先等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算使出那么卑鄙的手段 你还是想赢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想赢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别那么无情嘛 我们是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.69,0:18:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你愿意把电池拿去给韩森 那我就答应帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛一定要公平
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.78,0:18:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样重量还是没办法减轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.18,0:18:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:20.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这…这不是电池吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要有了这个 我就能战胜桑森了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把东西拿去给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就快完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.84,0:18:38.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这么一来我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:46.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在关节利用了磁铁 动作会很流畅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再来就是外表
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 就用黑色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,黑色？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:54.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为韩森是用红色的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后还要装上角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.85,0:18:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,装角只会变得更重耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.06,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 那样看起来比较强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 这下子我赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男人好讨厌喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明还有很多要紧的事该做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.11,0:19:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们却老是不务正业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太狡猾了 强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你竟然与桑森联手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.49,0:19:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们赢定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:36.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪边会赢呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两雄不并立 最后导致两败俱伤 大概就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.57,0:19:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,两败俱伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为两边都是用 同一张设计图制作出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,性能完全相同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:54.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就沿这座岛的海岸线跑一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先到的就算获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赢的会是我的黑色大王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:01.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是我的红色大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事要试了才知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.85,0:20:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就是知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们两个都给我听好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:11.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比赛结束之后就不要再吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.26,0:20:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这我明白\N这我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.27,0:20:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,预备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.12,0:20:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上啊\N冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.73,0:20:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都到了这种时候居然才给我跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.44,0:20:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们不追上去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要在这里等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的黑色大王就会自己回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对吧 强
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:08.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的红色大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.35,0:21:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只会直直的往前跑\N只会直直的往前跑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.86,0:21:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:18.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.76,0:21:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.57,0:21:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.38,0:21:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又不是你说停下来它就会停
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.35,0:21:40.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得这前面是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.35,0:21:44.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大海！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的发明…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的小型电池…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.93,0:21:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的小型电池…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.64,0:22:09.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追到了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.23,0:22:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.74,0:22:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.41,0:22:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.78,0:23:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都怪我们要吵架…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早知道会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,应该要对他更好一点才对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.62,0:23:22.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又还没确定他已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.39,0:23:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,害我这么担心他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.37,0:23:38.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.55,0:23:54.54,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:24:02.53,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.59,0:24:07.69,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:12.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:21.04,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:31.08,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.15,0:24:39.96,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.03,0:24:44.13,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:48.83,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.91,0:24:57.87,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.16,0:25:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要能将葛兰坦修好
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.76,0:25:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能离开这座漂流岛
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.26,0:25:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是却突然出现一大群蚊子 让我们没办法作业
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.93,0:25:19.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家因为被蚊子咬 一直吵着痒死了痒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.77,0:25:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为了制作驱虫药而潜入海中的我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.04,0:25:25.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却发现海底是以类似 铁制的东西所构成的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.44,0:25:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛真的不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.31,0:25:29.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『地底迷宫』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.71,0:25:30.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔
